        <updateDate>2021-01-14T19:30:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Department of Homeland Security Insider Threat and Mitigation Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) to establish an Insider Threat Program.</p> <p>Such program shall (1) provide training and education for DHS personnel to identify, prevent, mitigate, and respond to insider threat risks to DHS's critical assets; (2) provide investigative support regarding such threats; and (3) conduct risk mitigation activities for such threats.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
